Anthrax, Lesotho
----------------
Information received on [and dated] 17 Dec 2014 from Mrs Marosi Molomo, Director of Livestock Services, Ministry of Agriculture and Food Security, Department of Livestock Services, Maseru, Lesotho

Summary
Report type: Immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 11 Dec 2014
Date of pre-confirmation of the event: 11 Dec 2014
Report date: 17 Dec 2014
Date submitted to OIE: 17 Dec 2014
Reason for notification: Reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 6 Mar 2014
Manifestation of disease: Clinical disease
Causal agent: _Bacillus anthracis_
Nature of diagnosis: Laboratory (basic)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country

New outbreaks (2)
Outbreak 1: Mekaling, Phatlalla, Mohale's Hoek
Date of start of the outbreak: 11 Dec 2014
Outbreak status: Continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: Village
